                <h3 class="subheading">Expected Price and Launch Timeline</h3>
                <p>While Brixton Motorcycles has not announced a definitive launch date for the Crossfire 500 in India, industry sources and leaked information from their partners suggest that the official launch is imminent. The motorcycles are expected to hit the Indian market by October 2025. The festive season, with its historically high consumer spending, is a strong contender for the launch timeframe.<br /><br />
